- make sure the @api_schema.json and @db-schema.json files are always are always the source of truth for the API and database schema
- make sure the @get_endpoints.py and @post_endpoints.py files are always up to date with the api schema
- use poetry to run pytest
- remember to redeploy terraform whenever making changes to terraform, api handler, lambda code, adding s3 tables, or anything else that lives on aws
- remember, if you change @handler.py or @dynamodb.py you have to run terraform sync before testing again